r” he said of his first  years spent in killeen texas and greenville south carolina “i had a single mom who raised three boys on food stamps and by working two jobs to earn some money spearman began working at age  mowing lawns when he was  he created a second revenue stream by selling bubble gum to classmates so it has gone to the present day he never stopped thinking of new ways to make sure he had money coming in spearman is the first person in his immediate family to graduate from college he knew he wasn’t attending unless he paid for it himself so spearman applied for more than  scholarships got about  of them worth roughly  and graduated from the university of texas at austin in  between commencement and localeur’s liftoff spearman held several highprofile highintensity positions • he was the primary speechwriter for david paulison director of the federal emergency management agency in  and  sometimes he’d see president george w bush and secretary of homeland security michael chertoff using what he wrote to answer anderson cooper’s questions on cnn and he often attended briefings that included at least one of those three men • he was director of operations and strategic initiatives in  for bazaarvoice inc which powers consumer product reviews online spearman also cowrote a book published in  “real role models” which profiled “ highlevel black professionals” for the purpose of introducing africanamerican youth to role models outside the sports and entertainment sectors and he founded sneak attack llc a sneaker and urbanfashion company in  and style x the official style segment of south by southwest “i felt my creativity wasn’t activated until i became an entrepreneur” spearman said of his decision to leave corporate america and begin his own ventures “my plan was to found one business every year until one stuck” how do you relieve stress i actually like stress and high pressure but for fun i run longdistance races like halfmarathons go bowling and play a lot of pingpong i have a pingpong table in my front yard if you could be any superhero who would you be wolverine of the xmen he has a code he’s not perfect like superman he’s not wealthy like batman he’s usually on the side of good and right if you could play any sport professionally and be one of the best which sport would you pick and what position would you play pitcher for the atlanta braves if you could be a division i scholarship athlete at any school what sport would you choose and what school runner at the university of oregon i love steve prefontaine who would win in a fight homer simpson from “the simpsons” or mr mackey from “south park” homer simpson he did ok against peter griffin on family guy in that episode “the simpsons guy” what’s your favorite meal to eat at a restaurant breakfast what’s your favorite austin restaurant uchiko what’s your dream car ferrari  spider if you could have dinner with anyone whom you haven’t met who would it be donald glover he is a grammyaward nominated rapper and actor who will play a young lando calrissian in an upcoming “star wars” movie plus hes a comedian and was a writer for the tv show “ rock” joah spearman age  fiancé susannah residence austin hometowns killeen texas and greenville south carolina education bachelor of science in public relations university of texas at austin  email joahlocaleurcom mike cronin covers the technology startup and finance sectors in central texas for the austin business journal related content localeur to hire expand after raising m austinbased travel website expands nationally entrepreneurs criticize austins funding scene home of the day sponsor listing walk to tarrytown boat club see all homes of the day industries technology retailing  restaurants human resources suggested reading sponsored by people on the move img srchttpsmediabizjusviewimgcraigjepsonxxjpg altcraig jepson craig jepson toler law group pc img srchttpsmediabizjusviewimgjamesmassaroxxjpg altjames massaro james massaro civil